Class FilteredSet

java.lang.Object
  org.mundo.service.FilteredSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<ServiceInfo>, IRoutingService.IConn, IEmits, IReceiver
public class FilteredSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<ServiceInfo>, IReceiver, IRoutingService.IConn, IEmits

Encapsulates the result of a service query. Instances of FilteredSet are returned by the query functions of ServiceManager and are usually not instantiated directly from client code.

Loggers: svcrs

Author:
Erwin Aitenbichler
